《'''DRAMA'''》是[[韓國|韓國]]男子組合[[TXT_(組合)|TOMORROW X TOGETHER]]的第二張日語單曲<ref>{{cite news |title=TOMORROW X TOGETHER Announce 'DRAMA' CD Available In The U.S. September 25 Plus 3 Limited Edition Versions |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/tomorrow-x-together-announce-drama-cd-available-in-the-us-september-25-plus-3-limited-edition-versions-301112699.html |accessdate=2022-01-29 |work=www.prnewswire.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129160423/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/tomorrow-x-together-announce-drama-cd-available-in-the-us-september-25-plus-3-limited-edition-versions-301112699.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Armstrong |first1=Sam |title=Tomorrow X Together Announce New ‘Drama’ EP {{!}} uDiscover |url=https://www.udiscovermusic.com/news/tomorrow-x-together-drama-ep/ |accessdate=2022-01-29 |work=uDiscover Music |date=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129235320/https://www.udiscovermusic.com/news/tomorrow-x-together-drama-ep/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由[[房時赫|HITMAN BANG]]、{{link-ja|川合大介|KM-MARKIT|KM-MARKIT}}、Slow Rabbit作曲、{{link-ja|川合大介|KM-MARKIT|KM-MARKIT}}作詞，並在2020年8月19日以四個不同版本推出。<ref name=release>{{cite web|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/txt-release-drama-music-video-japanese-ep|title=TXT Release “Drama” Music Video, Japanese EP MOAs, it's finally here.|language=en|work=|publisher=|accessdate=2020-08-19|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818205102/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/txt-release-drama-music-video-japanese-ep|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
2020年6月24日，所屬經紀公司宣布TOMORROW X TOGETHER將在8月19日推出第二張日文單曲《DRAMA》，單曲《DRAMA》收錄了新歌《Everlasting Shine（永遠に光れ）》、 《Drama（日語版）》以及《Can't You See Me?（日語版）》三首歌曲，而《Everlasting Shine（永遠に光れ）》是TOMORROW X TOGETHER的第一首日文原創曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/6/24/n12208368.htm|title=TXT首度推出日文原創曲 新單曲8月19日發行|accessdate=2020-06-24|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710055754/https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/6/24/n12208368.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/922d4978d7251b981e38bd06fb207197417310f9|title=TOMORROW X TOGETHER、「Drama」MVを一部公開。楽曲の先行配信も決定|accessdate=2020-07-29|work=|language=ja|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729092147/https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/922d4978d7251b981e38bd06fb207197417310f9|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2020年7月29日，所屬經紀公司宣布新歌《Everlasting Shine（永遠に光れ）》為日本人氣動漫《[[黑色五葉草|黑色五葉草]]》的主題曲，成為該動漫第一首由[[韓國|韓國]]藝人演唱的主題曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.solotrust.com/read/30755/TXT-Nyanyikan-OST-Anime-Black-Clover-Everlasting-Shine|title=TXT Nyanyikan OST Anime Black Clover, Everlasting Shine|accessdate=2020-08-01|work=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116104921/https://solotrust.com/read/30755/TXT-Nyanyikan-OST-Anime-Black-Clover-Everlasting-Shine|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kpopmonster.jp/?p=56015|title=https://www.kpopmonster.jp/?p=56015|accessdate=2020-08-07|work=|language=ja|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110074049/https://www.kpopmonster.jp/?p=56015|dead-url=no}}</ref>

